    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Open up a build of Focus with the new splash screen.\r\n2. Observe the gradient direction.\r\n3. Rotate the device.\r\n4. Observe the gradient direction again.\r\n5. Open settings, then close it to return to the homescreen.\r\n6. Observe the gradient direction one more time\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n- At 4 and 6, the direction should be similar to the [landscape designs](https://www.figma.com/file/jgsM2hWimZbPmtUJn7IGIB/Landing-Page?node-id=2030%3A68481).\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\n- Only at 6, the direction is similar to the landscape designs.\r\n\r\n### Device information\r\n\r\n* Android device: All devices\r\n* Focus version: Happens on all varients, but the nightly gradient is easiest to notice.\r\n\r\n<!-- video of the bug\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1370580/133292128-4040542f-261c-42d9-b138-cf56db3deb2d.mp4\r\n-->\r\n\r\n\r\n",
